23 /// ilist_half_node - Base class that provides prev services for sentinels.
24 ///
25 template<typename NodeTy>
26 class ilist_half_node {
27  friend struct ilist_traits<NodeTy>;
28  NodeTy *Prev;
29 protected:
30  NodeTy *getPrev() { return Prev; }
31  const NodeTy *getPrev() const { return Prev; }
32  void setPrev(NodeTy *P) { Prev = P; }
33  ilist_half_node() : Prev(0) {}
34 };

39 /// ilist_node - Base class that provides next/prev services for nodes
40 /// that use ilist_nextprev_traits or ilist_default_traits.
41 ///
42 template<typename NodeTy>
43 class ilist_node : private ilist_half_node<NodeTy> {
44  friend struct ilist_nextprev_traits<NodeTy>;
45  friend struct ilist_traits<NodeTy>;
46  NodeTy *Next;
47  NodeTy *getNext() { return Next; }
48  const NodeTy *getNext() const { return Next; }
49  void setNext(NodeTy *N) { Next = N; }
50 protected:
51  ilist_node() : Next(0) {}
52 
53 public:
54  /// @name Adjacent Node Accessors
55  /// @{
56 
57  /// \brief Get the previous node, or 0 for the list head.
58  NodeTy *getPrevNode() {
59  NodeTy *Prev = this->getPrev();
60 
61  // Check for sentinel.
62  if (!Prev->getNext())
63  return 0;
64 
65  return Prev;
66  }
67 
68  /// \brief Get the previous node, or 0 for the list head.
69  const NodeTy *getPrevNode() const {
70  const NodeTy *Prev = this->getPrev();
71 
72  // Check for sentinel.
73  if (!Prev->getNext())
74  return 0;
75 
76  return Prev;
77  }
78 
79  /// \brief Get the next node, or 0 for the list tail.
80  NodeTy *getNextNode() {
81  NodeTy *Next = getNext();
82 
83  // Check for sentinel.

85  return 0;

89
